data.description: LARGEST LOT IN THE MEADOW RIDGE COMMUNITY! Welcome to this stunning 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in the coveted community of Meadow Ridge. Enjoy the luxury of space with the largest lot in Meadow Ridge, spanning over half an acre. Perfect for gardening, outdoor activities, or potential expansion. Situated on a quiet cul-de-sac, this property offers privacy, space, and picturesque sunset views. The kitchen features elegant granite countertops, adding a touch of sophistication to your culinary endeavors. A two-car garage provides ample space for vehicles and storage. Additionally, an attic space offers even more storage potential. The open-concept layout creates a seamless flow between living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it ideal for entertaining and family gatherings. Sliding doors lead to the backyard, creating a seamless transition to outdoor living. Perfect for barbecues, gatherings, or simply enjoying the serene surroundings. The seller is generously providing a one-year home warranty, offering peace of mind to the lucky buyer. A n in-house laundry room comes complete with a washer and dryer, adding to the convenience of this home. The master bedroom features a spacious walk-in closet, providing ample storage for your wardrobe and personal belongings. Situated near Lake Eustis and parks, outdoor enthusiasts will appreciate the proximity to natural beauty and recreational activities. Only an hour's drive from Disney World, Sea World, and Universal Studios, this home offers endless opportunities for entertainment. Plus, it's just a short drive to either coast for a day at the beach. Don't miss out on this exceptional property, where spacious living, modern amenities, and a prime location converge. Schedule your viewing today and experience the Meadow Ridge lifestyle for yourself!
